# This directory holds shipped + locally-trained model files.
#
# The committed proof-of-life model is `belgium-tiny.safetensors` plus
# its sidecar `belgium-tiny.safetensors.config.json`. Both files are
# under 5 MB combined and small enough to commit.
#
# Locally-trained models (other names) should be gitignored — see the
# repository root .gitignore.
